description: Banco Espírito Santo, S.A. is in the process of liquidation of its remaining assets. Previously, the company was engaged in banking operations. The company was formerly known as Banco Espírito Santo e Comercial de Lisboa and changed its name to Banco Espírito Santo, S.A. in 1999. Banco Espírito Santo, S.A. was founded in 1869 and is headquartered in Lisbon, Portugal.
